    • isSinglePlotWorld

      public static boolean isSinglePlotWorld(String worldName)
      Returns true if the given string matches the naming system used to identify single plot worlds e.g. -1_5 represents plot id *;-1;5. "*" being the plot area name given to single plot world PlotArea.
      Since:
      6.1.4
